Notes.Text:
This update contains KDE Frameworks 5.19.0 (boo#967668)

For details, see https://www.kde.org/announcements/kde-frameworks-5.19.0.php

The following bugs were fixed in specific packages: 

kxmlgui, kdelibs4support:
- boo#955280: session not restored after logout/login

kio:
- boo#963680: Unable to create new link to application - Install 'Create New' templates as a workaround
